subject: FW: Website Job Ads
preview: Hi Natalie, Hi Allie, Can you please tell me if the job listing in question is: "Small Animal Medicine Residency"? We suspect this is a caching issue where an old version of the page is being shown

full_threads.body:
Hi Natalie, Hi Allie, 

Can you please tell me if the job listing in question is: "Small Animal Medicine Residency"? 

We suspect this is a caching issue where an old version of the page is being shown on a particular device/computer. We have cleared the cache at our end, and the job listing shows when viewing the page in incognito mode.

action.text: Rica Rosario Valencia assigned to Joel Maligalig

full_threads.body:

Hope you're well!
We're having the same issue where the changes I'm making to our job ads aren't showing for some people. Our People and Culture team can't see the new listings when viewing the website but I can?
Could you look into this for us if it's a website issue?

See below as what Rachel can see (the old listings).

Thanks in advance.

I'm on leave from tomorrow so I've copied Allie in to help if you need anything. @Allie Loomis can you please let Rachel know the outcome?
